{"word":"Demons","slug":"demons","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Demons</b> Worship of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=7'>Lev 17:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=17'>Deu 32:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=15'>2Ch 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=37'>Psa 106:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=4&verse=9'>Mat 4:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=7'>Luk 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=46&chapter=10&verse=21'>1Co 10:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=54&chapter=4&verse=1'>1Ti 4:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=13&verse=4'>Rev 13:4</a><br/> Worship of, forbidden<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=7'>Lev 17:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=13&verse=2'>Zec 13:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=20'>Rev 9:20</a><br/> Possession by, instances of:<br/> - Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=16&verse=23'>1Sa 16:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=18&verse=11'>1Sa 18:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=19&verse=10'>1Sa 19:10</a> <br/> - Two men of the Gergesenes<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=8&verse=34'>Mat 8:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=5&verse=20'>Mar 5:20</a> <br/> - The dumb man<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=9&verse=33'>Mat 9:33</a> <br/> - The blind and dumb man<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=22'>Mat 12:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=11&verse=14'>Luk 11:14</a> <br/> - The